NAPA DETROIT - OCTOBER TRADE NEWSLETTER

Hello from your NAPA Detroit team,

Fall is here and the bays are busy. A few things worth a look this month for independent
shops like Dunn & Sons.

SEASONAL REMINDERS
- Battery testing season is on. Cold snaps are coming, get customers checked early.
- Brake and rotor demand climbs through November. Stock your fast movers now.
- Wiper and washer fluid pull-through is up. Good counter add-on.

TRAINING CORNER
Our ASE refresher webinars run every other Thursday evening. Diagnostics track this month
covers CAN bus fault tracing. Handy for your GearUp students if you want to point them at it.

SHOP TALK
Congratulations to the shops celebrating milestones this quarter. If you have a restoration
project you are proud of, send us a photo for the regional spotlight. We hear there is a
sweet Chevelle out your way.

This newsletter is informational only. Nothing here needs a reply.

Thanks for being a NAPA Pro partner,
NAPA Detroit
